    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch and the interior is still smelling fresh. It runs like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let it go. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
